{"tid":1212863,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"見到香港咁樣我真係好心痛","createTime":"2019-06-12T23:00:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-12T23:57:15.000Z","uid":212063,"like":72,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"897da600a0af2049f1670344774e628a64a589ae","tid":1212863,"uid":212063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T23:00:52.000Z","msg":"103萬人遊行 無視<br />\n萬人包圍立法會 武力清場<br />\n琴日由朝早開路比黑警拎盾拎棍追<br />\n到3點比佢地打 比佢地用催淚彈扔<br />\n我見到嘅係一班冇人性嘅警犬<br />\n同一班對未來有追求出嚟示威嘅人<br />\n呢個對比真係好大好大<br />\n警棍 催淚彈 胡椒噴霧等等<br />\n我全部都食哂<br />\n我一直都咗留係前線<br />\n睇到呢一切<br />\n我好驚嘅唔係武器<br />\n而係比送中條例通過到<br />\n我到依家兩隻手臂都仲有傷<br />\n抖氣都仲未順返<br />\n到依家訓唔著係點解？<br />\n係我見到嘅呢一切都令到我好心痛<br />\n啱啱見到6月13號姐係今日會回恢復二讀<br />\n我咁樣我今日都會再出去<br />\n我好希望大家唔好比琴日武力清場而打擊<br />\n我好希望今日可以見到大家<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香港人加油</span></span>"},{"pid":"1ff2f06896c76fe55ac3224632bec8ea679d2078","tid":1212863,"uid":212063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T23:14:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"99461d75e6054910929aca83bd9509f482153329","tid":1212863,"uid":212063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T23:14:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"dd08a7868a52cc0a3fee75eb687132b952050d66","tid":1212863,"uid":212063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T23:14:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4cf0ee49bea8ff1efb314158f5f4b765573cdaa7","tid":1212863,"uid":212063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T23:15:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9452ab0120012dd2616e1676f55c93840334e103","tid":1212863,"uid":208722,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T23:16:10.000Z","msg":"1030二讀，大家儘早到<br />\n班保皇狗分分鐘入埋去"},{"pid":"a4bf7d5b64eed63e9227a6de59898014f8cfcaf4","tid":1212863,"uid":83025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T23:18:26.000Z","msg":"樓主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好想攬下你<img src=\"/assets/